<link>https://www.jiscmail.ac.uk:443/cgi-bin/webadmin?A2=MIMAS-WOK;aac03056.1503</link>   <description> ** Apologies for cross-posting**<br><br>Upgrade to Endnote Online 10 March 2015<br><br>Please be advised that Thomson Reuters are releasing an update to Endnote Online on March 10 2015.<br>There will be no expected downtime or outage to Endnote Online as a result of the update with minimal impact to users.
